":5.8}],"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Japanese","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語"},{"english_name":"Thai","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย"}],"status":"Ended","tagline":"","type":"Scripted","vote_average":5.5,"vote_count":2}},"person_1324472_translations":{"at":1772689467324,"data":{"id":1324472,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"카와니시 켄고","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kengo Kawanishi (河西 健吾, Kawanishi Kengo, February 18, 1985) is a Japanese male voice actor. He was born in Osaka and his blood type is A. He was formerly affiliated with Office Kaoru, but is now affliated with Mause Promotion.\n\nHe debuted as a voice actor in 2006. In June 2010, he dubbed Sterling Knight for the first time as Christopher in \"Starstruck\", and in October 2015, he starred for the first time in the anime series \"Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans\" in the role of Augustus.\n\nChika Umino, the original author of \"March Comes In Like a Lion,\" described him as \"a shining dark voice.\"","name":"Kengo Kawanishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kengo Kawanishi (河西 健吾 Kawanishi Kengo, prefectura de Osaka, Japón, 18 de febrero de 1985) es un actor de voz japonés. En 2005, se graduó en la Amusement Media Academy e hizo su debut como actor de voz al año siguiente. En 2010, fue el doblador japonés del personaje de Christopher Wilde en la película Starstruck. Kawanishi formó parte de Office Kaoru hasta junio de 2012 y, tras trabajar un tiempo como artista independiente, se unió a Mausu Promotion en 2013.","name":"Kengo Kawanishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河西健吾是日本的男性聲優。出身於大阪府，畢業於娛樂傳媒綜合學院聲優部，所屬公司為 Mausu Promotion。","name":"河西健吾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"河西健吾","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河西健吾（かわにし けんご,Kawanishi Kengo），日本的男性配音演员，大阪府出生，所属事务所为Mausu Promotion。\n\n从小喜欢游戏和动画，由于高中是自动扶梯式的生活，感觉升入大学以后找工作的这种人生没有意思。为了探寻更有趣的世界而选择成为演员。之后来到AMG大阪校上学。\n\n父母是经营咖啡店的，受环境影响经常阅读漫画杂志。\n\n2006年以声优身份出道。\n\n2012年6月加入Office 薰事务所，2013年2月1日开始为Mausu Promotion所属。娱乐传媒综合学院声优部毕业。\n\n擅长关西腔。\n\n2015年在《机动战士高达 铁血的奥尔芬斯》中首次出演男一号三日月·奥古斯。\n\n最喜欢的作品是CLAMP的《魔法骑士》。\n\n与声优村田太志是好友。\n\n室内派，没有邀请的话在家中度过假期。常玩手游。","name":"河西健吾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kengo Kawanishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Kengo Kawanishi (河西 健吾, Kawanishi Kengo, né le 18 février 1985) est un acteur de voix japonais. Il est né à Osaka. Il était auparavant affilié à Office Kaoru, mais est maintenant affilié à Mause Promotion.\n\nIl a débuté en tant qu'acteur de voix en 2006. En juin 2010, il a doublé Sterling Knight pour la première fois en tant que Christopher dans \"Starstruck\", et en octobre 2015, il a joué pour la première fois dans la série animée \"Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans\" dans le rôle d'Augustus.\n\nChika Umino, l'auteur original de \"March Comes In Like a Lion\", l'a décrit comme ayant \"une voix sombre et éclatante.\"","name":"Kengo Kawanishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кэнго Каваниси","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"เค็งโงะ คาวานิชิ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kengo Kawaniši","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"Kengo Kawanishi (河西 健吾, Kawanishi Kengo) è un doppiatore giapponese. È nato il 18 febbraio 1985 a Osaka e il suo gruppo sanguigno è A. In precedenza affiliato a Office Kaoru, ora lavora per la Mause Promotion.\n\nHa debuttato come doppiatore nel 2006. Nel giugno 2010 ha doppiato per la prima volta Sterling Knight nel ruolo di Christopher in “Starstruck” e nell'ottobre 2015 ha recitato per la prima volta nella serie anime “Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans” nel ruolo di Augustus.\n\nChika Umino, l'autrice originale di “March Comes In Like a Lion”, lo ha descritto come “una splendente voce oscura”.","name":"Kengo Kawanishi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кенґо Каваніші","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河西健吾是日本的男性聲優。出身於大阪府。隸屬於 Mausu Promotion。","name":"河西健吾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kengo Kawanishi","primary":false}}]}},"person_1214870_translations":{"at":1772689469955,"data":{"id":1214870,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Tyler James Williams (born October 9, 1992) is an American actor and rapper. He is best known for playing the title character on the UPN/CW sitcom Everybody Hates Chris, songwriter Cyrus DeBarge in the Disney Channel movie Let It Shine, and Noah on AMC's The Walking Dead. He has also appeared in films such as Detroit and The United States vs. Billie Holiday.\n\nHe is a series regular on the workplace sitcom Abbott Elementary (2021-).","name":"Tyler James Williams","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Tyler James Williams é um ator, dublador e rapper estadunidense. Iniciou sua carreira como ator infantil, fazendo participações em Saturday Night Live, Little Bill e Sesame Street, até ganhar destaque interpretando o personagem-título, inspirado em Chris Rock, na sitcom Everybody Hates Chris.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Tyler James Williams est un acteur américain, né le 9 octobre 1992 dans le Comté de Westchester, dans l'état de New York.\n\nIl s’est fait connaître du grand public pour avoir incarné le personnage principal de la série télévisée comique Tout le monde déteste Chris (2005-2009), et devient le plus jeune acteur à recevoir un NAACP Image Awards1.\n\nIl fait partie de la distribution principale de quatre séries : La sitcom Go On (2012-2013), la série d'horreur The Walking Dead (2014-2015), la série policière Esprits criminels : Unité sans frontières (2016-2017) et la série d'action Whiskey Cavalier (2019).\n\nIl apparait également dans des longs métrages tels que Enfants non accompagnés (2006), Dear White People (2014), Detroit (2017) et Billie Holiday, une affaire d'État (2021).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拉伦西奇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"טיילר ג'יימס","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тайлер Джэймс Уільямс","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拉倫西奇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тайлер Джеймс Вільямс","primary":false}}]}}}}